null,{"className":"mb-6 flex items-center space-x-1 text-sm text-gray-400","children":[["$","div","/docs",{"className":"flex items-center","children":[false,["$","$L4",null,{"href":"/docs","className":"text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-200","children":"Docs"}]]}],["$","div","/docs/dobi",{"className":"flex items-center","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-chevron-right mx-1 h-4 w-4 text-gray-400","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","mthhwq",{"d":"m9 18 6-6-6-6"}],"$undefined"]}],["$","$L4",null,{"href":"/docs/dobi","className":"text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-200","children":"$$DOBI"}]]}],["$","div","/docs/dobi/ai-agent",{"className":"flex items-center","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-chevron-right mx-1 h-4 w-4 text-gray-400","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","mthhwq",{"d":"m9 18 6-6-6-6"}],"$undefined"]}],["$","$L4",null,{"href":"/docs/dobi/ai-agent","className":"font-medium text-white","children":"AI Agent"}]]}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 text-white","children":"DOBI - AI Agent"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose max-w-none","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-300","children":"DOBI is an innovative AI agent integrated within the Dobprotocol ecosystem. It is designed to enhance the management and validation of Real-World Assets (RWAs). By leveraging advanced algorithms, DOBI ensures data accuracy and reliability, fostering investor confidence in autonomous asset investments."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["A significant milestone for DOBI was its successful \"red pill\" in ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://app.virtuals.io/virtuals/13315","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"Virtuals.fun"}],", achieved in under 24 hours. This rapid deployment showcases the project's innovative capabilities and sets a precedent for future integrations within the blockchain ecosystem. DOBI's potential extends beyond current functionalities. Future enhancements will include capabilities to handle unstructured data and images, further solidifying its role as a validator within the ecosystem."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The development of these advanced features aims to revolutionize asset management by introducing Decentralized Autonomous Machines (DAMs), which will allow programmable profit flows under AI supervision."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 text-white","children":"Core Purpose"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Dobi's main purpose is to validate off-chain data to be used as oracles to approve transactions in profit pools. Additionally, Dobi will have full access to the asset's wallet, enabling it to contract services such as preventive maintenance, upgrades, or other necessary actions to ensure the continuous operation of the autonomous asset."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 text-white","children":"Key Features of DOBI"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Data Validation:"}]," DOBI verifies the integrity of data from RWAs, ensuring transparency and trustworthiness for investors. This validation process is critical for maintaining a secure investment environment."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Profit Distribution:"}]," As DOBI validates transactions, it generates rewards that are distributed among $DOBI token holders. This mechanism not only incentivizes participation but also aligns the interests of all stakeholders."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Collateral Reduction:"}]," Increased trust through DOBI's validations allows businesses to lower the collateral required for securing investments. This reduction makes it easier for investors to engage with autonomous assets."]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 text-white","children":"Join the transformation"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Engage with DOBI and experience a new standard in asset management. The integration of AI within Dobprotocol streamlines operations and enhances profitability and security for investors."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Discover how DOBI can elevate your investment strategy and join this groundbreaking initiative in blockchain technology."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 text-white","children":"Future Developments with DOBI"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The DOBI team is continuously working on expanding its capabilities. Future developments will focus on:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Enhanced processing of unstructured data and images for more comprehensive validation"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Advanced pattern recognition for early detection of potential issues with RWAs"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Deeper integration with various blockchain networks to expand reach and applicability"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improved AI decision-making algorithms for autonomous asset management"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Development of more sophisticated smart contract interactions"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-4 text-white","children":"Technical Implementation"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"DOBI operates through a combination of:"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Trusted Execution Environments (TEEs) for secure data processing"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Machine learning algorithms trained on real-world IoT data"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Smart contract automation for profit distribution and governance"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Cryptographic validation mechanisms for data integrity"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"This technical foundation ensures that DOBI can reliably validate data from autonomous assets while maintaining the highest standards of security and privacy."}]]}]]}],"$undefined",null,["$","$L8",null,{"children":["$L9","$La",null]}]]}],{},null,false]},null,false]},null,false]},null,false]},null,false],["$","$1","h",{"children":[null,["$","$1","wryT1pL42ddFRD5J5qeuX",{"children":[["$","$Lb",null,{"children":"$Lc"}],["$","meta",null,{"name":"next-size-adjust","content":""}]]}],["$","$Ld",null,{"children":"$Le"}]]}],false]],"m":"$undefined","G":["$f","$undefined"],"s":false,"S":true}
